{"tid":1771271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女童肛門噴血「爸爸手弄的」","createTime":"2019-12-05T18:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T02:45:14.000Z","uid":3522,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"45475b428877f0a89a4f7ff78ae72e3149d613e1","tid":1771271,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:11:30.000Z","msg":"台中市一名年僅6歲的女童小晴（化名），107年間上幼稚園時被老師發現肛門出血，當園長詢問「為什麼流血」時，小晴支支吾吾地回答「是爸爸洗澡時用手弄的」，嚇得園方急忙向警方通報。檢警介入偵辦後，認為小晴生父阿明（化名）涉有重嫌，依法將他起訴。全案經一、二審後仍是疑點重重，加上小晴對於供詞前後不一，相當矛盾，且醫師也診斷可能是痔瘡、或是便祕造成肛裂，因此才會出血；台中高分院審理後駁回上訴，判決阿明無罪確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191205/1595222.htm#ixzz67G134stT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20191205%2F1595222.htm%23ixzz67G134stT&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=4347d334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191205/1595222.htm#ixzz67G134stT</a>"},{"pid":"2bb43fa72ae291b0e3dfe1a3f27b1f32ce477f02","tid":1771271,"uid":3522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:14:16.000Z","msg":"咁細個生痔瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17218b1e63be9137e24e5d30ff0694c85a03300c","tid":1771271,"uid":258578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84c945303cfa9ca83633b1d9c8eb07e456c11d72","tid":1771271,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"咁搞法d男人點敢幫手湊仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855ba5822ad4e74d3a7107f7a1f93329a76147dc","tid":1771271,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"台灣又得分"},{"pid":"d77c7a5d1655e727a194adbcb78d92242c59083a","tid":1771271,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"855ba5822ad4e74d3a7107f7a1f93329a76147dc","tid":1771271,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited